    • setTrustAnchorBPPolicy

      public void setTrustAnchorBPPolicy(boolean trustAnchorBPPolicy)
      Allows to set the trust anchor policy to use when creating -B and -LT levels. NOTE: when trust anchor baseline profile policy is defined only the certificates previous to the trust anchor are included when building -B level.
      Parameters:
